üß† Operational Summary

- Flow: Authorization Code Grant using OpenID Connect
- Initiator: Cloudflare Access
- Target Resource: Microsoft Graph API
- Session Metadata:
  - nonce: Replay protection
  - aud: Audience hash for token validation
  - idpId: Identity provider UUID
  - mtlsauth: Mutual TLS not used (certpresented: false)
  - auth_status: NONE (no prior auth)
  - redirectURL: /warp (Cloudflare internal routing)
  - appSessionHash: Session integrity marker

This is a federated login handshake between Cloudflare Access and Azure AD, requesting a code to later exchange for tokens to access Microsoft Graph.
